Summary: Extremely bright reflective sphere crosses in front of the moon then disappears
divs: Sighting DetailsI was at Steilacoom Park walking my dog and while looking at the moon I noticed a extremely bright spherical object to the NW. It looked like it was reflecting the sun. It traveled at a steady speed, crossed in front of the moon, continued to the the SW then instantly disappeared. Here's a text I sent right after the event. Yo.. I just saw a round ufo right now bro!! In front of the moon. Round, bright round shape moving just disappeared while I was watching. It looked like the sun was reflecting off it.. man it was crazy to see it just disappear. Moving and then gone. Just gone lol...
